{"tid":1874523,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"口交部 : 中國經濟下行世界必然動盪 為中國 為世界 國際應團結抗疫","createTime":"2020-02-11T08:58:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T09:46:16.000Z","uid":21470,"like":5,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"02db2c52ae00314b71fd27176cbd5f72b68811ad","tid":1874523,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T08:58:58.000Z","msg":"外交部指中國經濟長期向好不會因疫情而改變<br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部回應部分金融機構認為，新型肺炎疫情對中國經濟的影響，將產生骨牌效應，衝擊全球供應鏈，拉低世界經濟增長。發言人耿爽表示，中國經濟的基本面及長期向好趨勢，不會因為疫情而改變，中方有能力將影響降至最低。<br />\n<br />\n耿爽說，如果中國經濟受衝擊，必然會波及其他國家，世界經濟亦必然受影響，中國抗疫鬥爭既是為自己，亦是為世界，支持中國、幫助中國，亦是維護國際社會共同利益。<br />\n<br />\n耿爽強調，以鄰為壑保護不了自己，過度反應只會適得其反，當務之急是國際社會團結戰勝疫情，盡快恢復國家之間的正常交往合作，才能夠為世界經濟穩定增長提供有力支撐，釋放正面預期。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1507918-20200211.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1507918-20200211.htm&d=e9hI6ag5UTzhCSVhase9yCKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=7e6c8e58\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1507918-20200211.htm&h=f5aca060\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1507918-20200211.htm</a>"},{"pid":"e06ba16d67eced853d59d0936d39b82c455dcbab","tid":1874523,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T08:59:50.000Z","msg":"作數點夠你鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c4c6feff7b0c09a82c956cc4b25a3ff3a9bdce1","tid":1874523,"uid":41545,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T09:00:43.000Z","msg":"你個仆街遲早都禍延全球<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就依家殺左支那戒毒先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42a5d84b6d1b07007474b128632a01970f28fe0b","tid":1874523,"uid":134942,"like":3,"disli